    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Written treatises, or the records of a discourse on a subject, usually prepared and presented as the final requirement for a degree or diploma and typically based on independent research and giving evidence of the candidate's mastery of the subject and of scholarly method.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
